{"id":"mc1k70bnfo8b73lly2l","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>新波普风格示例</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4081, #ffcc00);\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px;\n        }\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .card {\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n            color: #333;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin: 10px;\n        }\n        button {\n            background-color: #ff4081;\n            border: none;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            display: inline-block;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            margin: 4px 2px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        button:hover {\n            background-color: #ffcc00;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1>欢迎来到新波普风格的世界！</h1>\n    <div class=\"card\">\n        <p>这是一个示例卡片，展示了新波普风格的设计元素。</p>\n        <button>点击我</button>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>","createdAt":"2025-06-18T06:16:23.667Z"}